      "content": "stop trying... i dont even know what that looks like. like, if i stop pretending, i just fall apart. there's no real me underneath the mask, just this empty feeling. everything is just so hollow. i keep thinking about what would happen if i just... didn't have to carry it anymore. if everything just went quiet.",
